title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Add a table to the report.
2. Include a group row in the table with a highlight rule and a map rule.
3. Preview the report.
4. Export the data from the table.
